&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3-5 years of lifecycle, CRM, or retention marketing experience at a consumer tech company or high growth startup&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands on experience with a major lifecycle or CRM platform such as Braze, Iterable, Klaviyo, or similar&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience building and scaling SMS programs alongside email (compliance, deliverability, sequencing)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong instincts on messaging, sequencing, and user psychology, you understand how to move someone from curious to committed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have a strong analytical mind and are comfortable pulling your own data, building reports, and letting results drive decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong writing skills with a high bar for both clarity and tone&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
